main()
  ↓
DownloadManager.run()
  ↓
self.process_downloads()  ← Orchestrator: Sets up queue & 4 workers
  ├─ Starts display_thread
  ├─ Populates download_queue with links
  ├─ Starts 4 download_worker threads
  └─ Waits for completion & cleanup
       ↓
    download_worker(slot_id)  ← Called 4 times (one per slot)
       ├─ Loops: Gets item from queue
       ├─ For each URL:
       │   ↓
       │   self.process_download(line_num, url, slot_id)  ← Handles single download
       │   ├─ Checks for existing file
       │   ├─ Verifies size
       │   ├─ Retry loop with wget -c
       │   └─ Returns (success, status)
